{"word":"ἐργαστέος","slug":"ἐργαστέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐργαστέος</b></el> <el>(ἐργαστέος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:ἐργάζομαι'><el>ἐργάζομαι</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one must work the land</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>τοὖργον ἔστ' ἐργ.</el> it <i>must be done</i> or <i>one must do</i> it, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}